From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: experintellia <280144245+experintellia@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Mon, 6 Jul 2026 22:34:43 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 06/16] wasm: read the JS clock everywhere std::time panics

std::time::{SystemTime,Instant}::now() abort on wasm32-unknown-unknown.
- rustls: JsClockTimeProvider via ClientConfig::builder_with_details
  (cert validation calls UnixTime::now during the handshake)
- tools: time_now() returns a wasm-safe Instant; Time::now call sites
  switched; path_is_dir/path_is_file sync-fs helpers for wasm
- deltachat-ratelimit: SystemTime::now via deltachat_time
